jsonvalues

Interface JsObj

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,JsElem>>, JsElem, Json<JsObj>, java.io.Serializable

    public interface JsObj
extends Json<JsObj>, java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,JsElem>>
    Represents a json object, which is an unordered set of name/element pairs. Two implementations are provided, an immutable which uses the persistent Scala HashMap, and a mutable which uses the conventional Java HashMap.
